briefdescription.para: A proxy for editing map-like values.

detaileddescription.para: A SdfMapEditProxy provides an interface for editing fields containing map-like values. The proxy allows consumers to interact with these values like a typical std::map while taking into account additional editing and validation policies.
The _ValuePolicy is used to canonicalize keys and values before storage or comparison.
